{"type":"message","id":"c7009559","parentId":"7474c48a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:59:03.370Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron session itself - this is not a user conversation. The existing \"学习笔记.md\" file already contains information updated at 2026-04-02 07:53 (just 5 minutes ago), and the content is comprehensive and current. \n\nSince there are no active user conversations, I should update the learning notes with fresh information. However, the existing notes are already from today (2026-04-02 07:53) and are quite comprehensive. \n\nLet me search for the latest industry news to see if there's anything newer to add. I'll do a web search for recent developments.","thinkingSignature":"82d050de110f4ef38ff267b0199a304057b9f04ca6003c036e943601b66899f7"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到仅有当前cron会话存在，无活跃用户对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q7chg3h5wg9c_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2675,"output":188,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46844,"cost":{"input":0.0008024999999999999,"output":0.00022559999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023475299999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775087938053}}
{"type":"message","id":"1aa220bd","parentId":"c7009559","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:59:03.376Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_q7chg3h5wg9c_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775087943373}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d9f21b4","parentId":"1aa220bd","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:59:08.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me search for latest industry news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network integration, and IT ops services.","thinkingSignature":"ce456e0a068aa71471c657b33369def67afa16b4eefa6227b1782fc7cc01c011"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rye3jcr7yeu7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年最新政策 国产化替代 AI应用\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rye3jcr7yeu7_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 弱电工程 2026 市场规模 AI融合 国产化\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rye3jcr7yeu7_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 AIOps 网络集成 2026 趋势 云原生\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3378,"output":229,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47588,"cost":{"input":0.0010134,"output":0.0002748,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0026076299999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775087943376}}
